<div id="community-vibe">
    <h2 class="sect-title">Community Vibe in Ramsay </h2>
    <div class="col-grid-2">
        <div>
            <p class="par-lg">Named after a property owner and land agent called William Thomson Ramsay in 1956, the
                community in Ramsay has an area development plan in place. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Ramsay Real Estate is highly desirable among potential homebuyers as well as real estate
                investors who are looking to get their hand on a lucrative property with a great location. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">Homes for sale in Ramsay include an eclectic mix of housing options including townhomes,
                duplexes, bungalows, split level units, two storey homes and even apartment condominiums. </p>
            <p class="par-lg">There are a variety of options for all kinds of homebuyers from $600,000 detached single
                family homes to the premium bungalows priced upto $2 million as well. </p>
            <p class="par-xl">Most of the homebuyers are attracted to the neighborhood given its prime location with
                respect to shopping malls, recreational venues and public transportation facilities that are just a
                stoneâ€™s throw away.</p>

